{"tid":653946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中英街1號】5月31日上畫 三場優先場零宣傳離奇暴滿","createTime":"2018-05-05T07:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T05:11:10.000Z","uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"492a532fb553278fd4d7ae4c26820d7df8f81d76","tid":653946,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:44:02.000Z","msg":"趙崇基執導、游學修、廖子妤同盧鎮業主演嘅電影《中英街1號》，先後參加過日本大阪亞洲電影節及意大利鳥甸尼遠東電影節，喺大阪仲贏咗最優秀作品大賞。<br />\n<br />\n之前《中英街1號》喺香港一直上映無期，該片揚威海外之後，終於露出曙光，本月舉行了三場優先場，好快已經賣晒飛。趙崇基導演一直擔心冇戲院敢排片嘅問題，最後都解決咗。<br />\n<br />\n另一喜訊係，《中英街1號》已經安排咗本月31日在港上映，雖然檔期唔係特別好，始終可以同觀眾見到面。<br />\n<br />\n噚日套戲喺銅鑼灣舉行慶功，台前幕後連嘉賓有過百人出席，陶傑、黎小田，仲有藝發局副主席李偉民。趙崇基今日接受《蘋果》電話訪問，就稱唔係因為攞獎先至慶功：「都想借個機會多謝一班台前幕後工作人員，好多冇收錢咁幫我手。依家可以安排到5月31日上，好似發緊夢咁。」<br />\n<br />\n趙崇基又表示，《中英街1號》在大阪奪獎，且晉身外國電影節，加上三場優先場都好快爆晒，院商覺得有可為，所以肯排片上映，現在暫定有6間戲院上，趙崇基謂希望貴精不貴多。<br />\n<br />\n《中英街1號》故事涉及六七暴動，及香港社會運動（戲中虛擬2019年再發生「菜園村」事件翻版），引發不少爭議及傳聞，例名有傳該片每場優先場都被秒殺，係因為有啲「有心人」用唔想普羅市民睇到套戲，所以極速買晒啲飛。<br />\n<br />\n對於「包場」傳聞，趙崇基導演表示未有所聞：「其實每場優先場我都會出席，每次散場後，都見到唔同年齡層嘅人，有上年紀嘅，仲有好多後生仔，唔似嚟自同一個族群，所以我相信呢個傳聞唔可信。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/154349_ff7bf04d99aa5c34aa2fe64b3ae1124e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F154349_ff7bf04d99aa5c34aa2fe64b3ae1124e.png&h=526afd6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/154351_98ea5eefa183c4f41932ecbd6cc1acc3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F154351_98ea5eefa183c4f41932ecbd6cc1acc3.png&h=e69e76e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/154354_a33e8fd0c430aed0e1b9e243ab8e287b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F154354_a33e8fd0c430aed0e1b9e243ab8e287b.png&h=7b6e27ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n噚日套戲喺銅鑼灣舉行慶功<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180505/58152069\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F58152069&d=ZrrFDRUuioFNkS1lvnVcl04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=dd9d8618\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F58152069&h=10f8f0d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180505/58152069</a>"},{"pid":"103b603e18ad93a169b52e0e62a01ef3dc6fdf77","tid":653946,"uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:57:57.000Z","msg":"出年金像獎又要被河蟹"},{"pid":"14596dea6def8ed0e9152cdc8165c34fd6a08514","tid":653946,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T08:04:59.000Z","msg":"Btw條女幾秀氣<br />\n文青過另一件所謂文青女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d6508fa7834b3e470cfa40fb9cee5938980cbf","tid":653946,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T08:47:25.000Z","msg":"白頭佬又幾有型"},{"pid":"93af935d2c81adf43932a975f232851e44b69675","tid":653946,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T09:01:34.000Z","msg":"遲下好似消失的檔案咁，各組織book場播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7630f4cbd6457f4fcc68e782650de378cd5aede","tid":653946,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"103b603e18ad93a169b52e0e62a01ef3dc6fdf77","tid":653946,"uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:57:57.000Z","msg":"出年金像獎又要被河蟹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T09:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f52891cefc09e614daef7a7f35f2516848a4f2","tid":653946,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited